{"id": "art-15318", "label": "Art. 15318", "title": "Art. 15318", "slug": "art-15318", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_782548055\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2063\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_782548055\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>18</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_620226768\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2062\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_620226768\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Remunera&#355;ia</span> membrilor\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sau ai consiliului\nde supraveghere este stabilit&#259; prin actul constitutiv sau prin\nhot&#259;râre a adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1799670894\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2061\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1799670894\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Remunera&#355;ia</span>\nsuplimentar&#259; a membrilor consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nsau ai consiliului de supraveghere <span class=SpellE>îns&#259;rcina&#355;i</span>\ncu <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ii</span> specifice în cadrul organului\nrespectiv, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;ia</span>\ndirectorilor, în sistemul unitar, ori a membrilor directoratului, în sistemul\ndualist, sunt stabilite de consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv de consiliul de supraveghere. Actul constitutiv sau adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> fixeaz&#259;\nlimitele generale ale tuturor <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;iilor</span>\nacordate în acest fel.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1607531902\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2060\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1607531902\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Orice alte avantaje pot fi acordate numai în\nconformitate cu alin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_242314177\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2059\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_242314177\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Adunarea general&#259;, respectiv consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sau consiliul de supraveghere <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este cazul, comitetul de remunerare se\nvor asigura, la stabilirea <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;iilor</span> sau a\naltor avantaje, c&#259; acestea sunt justificate în raport cu îndatoririle\nspecifice ale persoanelor respective <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> economic&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}